{"tid":2073304,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"《中國日報》歐洲分部主管：孟晚舟的命比加拿大公民的命值錢太多了（孟命貴）","createTime":"2020-06-21T08:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T07:51:19.000Z","uid":48040,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a5df264911d0c3832db4826e889c57ab89126569","tid":2073304,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T08:18:35.000Z","msg":"6月20日，《中國日報》歐洲分部主管陳衛華在Twitter上回覆華爾街日報的記者說，比起那兩個在中國被捕的加拿大人的命，孟晚舟的命值錢不止10倍。但陳衛華現在已經刪除了該條Twitter。<br />\n<br />\nKovrig 以及 Spavor是加拿大人，在孟晚舟在加拿大被捕後，他們被指刺探中國秘密情報而在中國被捕，自2018年起被扣押至今。<br />\n<br />\n「People often fail to note that Meng is worth 10 Kovrig &amp; Spavor, if not more.」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ti7D07V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTi7D07V.jpg&h=55b5406c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n======<br />\n黃channel撐得好辛苦，可以幫手subscribe嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/e7Q0NLD83eI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fe7Q0NLD83eI&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Y5ugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=761b454f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/e7Q0NLD83eI</a>"},{"pid":"651432062617fdf53d04dfce05081dda05ab7448","tid":2073304,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T08:25:56.000Z","msg":"幫佢推到全世界見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引渡全球政府同議會（尤其美國）對付支那以及滅共</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛、熱狗放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國凌遲式消除香港作為支那獲得外資渠道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"ca701d6e83aa8508678454db2de884bb13d992ed","tid":2073304,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T08:30:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f67f59e409ca8531193eb3f35413a9b915b2a33a","tid":2073304,"uid":232185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T08:49:15.000Z","msg":"twitter for iphone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb8286fc688111cda44c738daa1186e5997a037","tid":2073304,"uid":232185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T09:39:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/chenweihua/status/1274291933108633600\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchenweihua%2Fstatus%2F1274291933108633600&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Y5ugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=3a669e93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchenweihua%2Fstatus%2F1274291933108633600&h=1794a3f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/chenweihua/status/1274291933108633600</a><br />\n刪咗但係仲認有做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/JChengWSJ/status/1274326383473438722\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJChengWSJ%2Fstatus%2F1274326383473438722&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Y5ugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=d305e6bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJChengWSJ%2Fstatus%2F1274326383473438722&h=ae09ffca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/JChengWSJ/status/1274326383473438722</a><br />\n唔該煲大佢"},{"pid":"278fcc3c6971d11a29ba3f34d7e2e09e497c2658","tid":2073304,"uid":51701,